## AWS Load Balancer (Ingress)
################################
# the following configuration allows the creation of an Ingress of type 'Load Balancer' within EKS.
# Documentation - https://github.com/aws/eks-charts/tree/master/stable/aws-load-balancer-controller 
# Additional configuration has to be set in order to complete this setup. (View documentation above)
